            "alt": "Tsukicomi26May \/ \u30de\u30f3\u30ac\u6295\u7a3f\u4f01\u753b\u300e\u30c4\u30ad\u30b3\u30df\u301c\u3075\u308f\u3075\u308f\u301c\u300f\u958b\u50ac \/ May 1st, 2026",
            "titleCaptionTranslation": {
              "workTitle": "Tsukicomi Manga Contest: Fluffy",
              "workCaption": "Greetings from pixiv.\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003EFrom Friday\u0026#44; May 1st\u0026#44; 2026\u0026#44; we are holding the manga posting project \u201cTsukicomi Manga Contest: Fluffy\u201d.\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003EIn this monthly event\u0026#44; we\u2019re inviting creators to take on monthly manga challenges by regularly introducing new themes.\u003Cbr \/\u003EDraw all kinds of soft and fluffy things: fluffy creatures\u0026#44; people with a soft and airy vibe\u0026#44; petals drifting gently\u0026#44; light and fluffy clothing\u0026#44; fluffy foods\u0026#44; that light and floaty feeling\u0026#44; dust drifting in the air\u0026#44; bubbles floating along\u2026\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003EAny manga that fits the theme is welcome.\u003Cbr \/\u003EYou can also pick a template and draw just one panel!\u003Cbr \/\u003E10 winners will be chosen by raffle from among all participants to receive a gift of their choice: an Amazon gift card (1000 JPY value) or pixivcoban (1500 JPY value).\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u25a0Event Period\u003Cbr \/\u003EFrom Friday\u0026#44; May 1st\u0026#44; to Sunday\u0026#44; May 31st\u0026#44; 2026\u0026#44; 11:59 pm JST\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u25a0How to Participate\u003Cbr \/\u003ECreate your manga based on the theme and submission format\u0026#44; then upload it to pixiv during the event period with the contest tag #Tsukicomi26May.\u003Cbr \/\u003EThere are no restrictions on the format for submitting your manga. It must include at least one panel with illustrations and dialogue\u0026#44; with no upper limit on the number of panels.\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003E*You may submit more than one entry\u0026#44; but one submission (e.g. one series) counts as one work. (Submitting the same work multiple times is not allowed\u0026#44; and submitting multiple works will not increase your chances of winning.)\u003Cbr \/\u003E*You may also enter the contest with a series\u0026#44; but please note that if you\u0026#39;re selected as a winner\u0026#44; one series counts as one entry.\u003Cbr \/\u003E*You can submit unfinished works.\u003Cbr \/\u003E*Works containing inappropriate content for underage individuals should be marked as R-18 or R-18G.\u003Cbr \/\u003E*Only works posted after Friday\u0026#44; May 1st\u0026#44; 2026\u0026#44; 12:00 am JST will be eligible for the raffle.\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u25a0Eligible Participants\u003Cbr \/\u003EThis contest is open to all registered pixiv users who have read and agreed to these Application Guidelines.\u003Cbr \/\u003E*Entries from companies and multiple creators will not be accepted.\u003Cbr \/\u003E*Underage contestants must obtain the consent of a guardian before entering.\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u25a0Entering from outside of Japan\u003Cbr \/\u003E(1) Contestants from outside of Japan are welcome to participate. Please make sure to read the Application Guidelines.\u003Cbr \/\u003E(2) If a winner outside of Japan is selected\u0026#44; the winner will receive an alternative prize of pixiv original merch (clear file folder).\u003Cbr \/\u003E(3) In certain cases\u0026#44; it may not be possible to ship the prize outside of Japan. In this case\u0026#44; the winner will not be eligible to receive the prize.\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u25a0Prizes\u003Cbr \/\u003E10 winners by raffle\u003Cbr \/\u003EAn Amazon gift card (1000 JPY value) or pixivcoban (1500 JPY value)\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003E*This campaign is sponsored by pixiv Inc.\u003Cbr \/\u003E*Amazon\u0026#44; Amazon.co.jp\u0026#44; and its logo are registered trademarks of Amazon.com\u0026#44; Inc.\u003Cbr \/\u003E*If you choose the pixivcoban\u0026#44; 1500 coban (free) will be granted.\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003ETry your hand at the \u201cFluffy\u201d theme! We are looking forward to your participation.\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u25c6 View All Entries\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https:\/\/www.pixiv.net\/contest\/Tsukicomi26May\u0022 target=\u0022_blank\u0022\u003Ehttps:\/\/www.pixiv.net\/contest\/Tsukicomi26May\u003C\/a\u003E"
            },
