            "useWordCount": true,
            "description": "Greetings from pixiv.\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003EThe pixiv Global Flash Fiction Challenge opens on Monday\u0026#44; April 27th\u0026#44; 2026!\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003ETo celebrate the recent pixiv Novel update for global writers\u0026#44; a submission challenge is being held for novel creators worldwide who write in languages other than Japanese. This project invites short stories of up to 1000 words (or 2000 characters)\u0026#44; created using the novel cover feature.\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003EThe theme is \u0026quot;secrets\u0026quot;.\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003EUnspoken feelings kept deep inside\u0026#44; small lies hidden in everyday life\u0026#44; or a grand mystery that could shake the world\u2026 We invite all kinds of stories inspired by the theme of \u0026quot;secrets\u0026quot;.\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003EFrom all participants\u0026#44; 10 winners will be selected by lottery to receive a curated set of premium Japanese stationery! Selected works will also be featured on official pixiv social media.\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003EEvent Period\u003Cbr \/\u003EMonday\u0026#44; April 27th - Sunday\u0026#44; May 31st\u0026#44; 2026\u0026#44; 11:59 pm JST\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003ETheme\u003Cbr \/\u003EWe\u0026#39;re looking for novels on the theme of secrets. All types of work and all genres are welcome.\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003EEntry Format\u003Cbr \/\u003ESubmit your work using pixiv\u0026#39;s novel posting feature\u0026#44; set the language of your novel accordingly (must be a language other than Japanese)\u0026#44; add a title using the novel cover feature\u0026#44; and include the participation tag pixivFlash26.\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003EEntry tag (required): pixivFlash26\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003ELength Requirements\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u30fbWord-based languages: 1000 words\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u30fbCharacter-based languages: 2000 words\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003E*Only works submitted on or after Monday\u0026#44; April 27th\u0026#44; 2026\u0026#44; at midnight JST are eligible for the lottery.\u003Cbr \/\u003E*You can submit unfinished works.\u003Cbr \/\u003E*If your work contains content inappropriate for minors\u0026#44; please mark it as R-18 or R-18G.\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003EEligible Participants\u003Cbr \/\u003EThis contest is open to all registered pixiv users who have read and agreed to these Application Guidelines.\u003Cbr \/\u003E*Works set to Japanese in the novel language settings will not be eligible for the lottery.\u003Cbr \/\u003E*Works posted by companies or multiple creators will not be eligible for the lottery.\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003EContest Terms\u003Cbr \/\u003EWorks that fall under the conditions listed below will be disqualified.\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u30fbWorks set to Japanese in the novel language settings.\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u30fbWorks without the contest tag attached.\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u30fbWorks over the character\/word limit.\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u30fbWorks posted before Sunday\u0026#44; April 26th\u0026#44; 2026\u0026#44; at 11:59 pm JST.\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003EPrizes\u003Cbr \/\u003E10 winners by lottery\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u30fbA curated set of premium Japanese stationery\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u30fbFeatured promotion on official pixiv social media accounts\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003EWe\u0026#39;re looking forward to your entries.\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u25c6 Contest Overview: \u003Ca href=\u0022https:\/\/www.pixiv.net\/novel\/contest\/pixivflash26\u0022 target=\u0022_blank\u0022\u003Ehttps:\/\/www.pixiv.net\/novel\/contest\/pixivflash26\u003C\/a\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u25c6 pixiv Novels Editorial Team official account: \u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https:\/\/www.pixiv.net\/en\/users\/43826688\u0022\u003Euser\/43826688\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u25c6 pixiv Novels Editorial Team X: \u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https:\/\/twitter.com